'''肖恩的瘋狂世界'''(Sean Saves the World)為一部美國[[情境喜劇|情境喜劇]]，由[[肖恩·海斯|肖恩·海斯]]主演。本部喜劇由[[NBC|NBC]]製播。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/nbc-starts-ordering-new-series-crisis-about-a-boy-picked-up/|title=NBC New Series Pickups: Sean Hayes, DJ Nash, 'Crisis', 'About A Boy', 'Believe'|date=May 9, 2013|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=May 11, 2013|archive-date=2013-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130519233156/http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/nbc-starts-ordering-new-series-crisis-about-a-boy-picked-up/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 本部影集於2013年10月3日首映，每個星期四晚間九點。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/06/21/nbc-announces-fall-premiere-dates-for-new-season-628112/20130621nbc01/|title=NBC Announces Fall Premiere Dates for New Season|date=June 21, 2013|work=The Futon Critic|accessdate=July 3, 2013|archive-date=2020-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200518055526/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/06/21/nbc-announces-fall-premiere-dates-for-new-season-628112/20130621nbc01//|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2014年1月28日，報導指出本劇取消。<ref name=cancellation>{{cite web|title=NBC Cancels 'Sean Saves the World'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/nbc-cancels-sean-saves-world-675161|work=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=January 28, 2014|author=Lesley Goldberg|coauthors=Michael O'Connell|date=January 28, 2014|archive-date=2014-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331090331/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/nbc-cancels-sean-saves-world-675161|dead-url=no}}</ref> 原先預訂了18集，已經拍攝了15集，剩下的集數將不再繼續製作。<ref name=cancellation/><ref>{{cite web|last=Nilles|first=Billy|title='Sean Saves the World' shuts down Season 1 production early|url=http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2014/01/sean-saves-the-world-shuts-down-season-1-production-early.html|work=Zap2it|accessdate=January 28, 2014|date=January 28, 2014|archive-date=2014-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131172611/http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2014/01/sean-saves-the-world-shuts-down-season-1-production-early.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2014年3月24日，未在電視播出的14與15集上傳至 iTunes 上供觀眾選購。

台灣由[[DIVA_Universal|DIVA Universal]]頻道於2014年2月4日起首映。

==劇情大綱==
肖恩(Sean)是一個離婚單親父親，同時是一位同性戀。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/05/10/sean-hayes-sean-saves-the-world_n_3254804.html |title=Sean Hayes To Star In 'Sean Saves The World,' As NBC Picks Up Gay Actor's New Sitcom |date=May 10, 2013 |last=Rudolph |first=Christoper |work=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]] |accessdate=May 11, 2013 |archive-date=2014-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201175845/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/05/10/sean-hayes-sean-saves-the-world_n_3254804.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 雖然事業有成，然而卻來了一個相當惹人厭的老闆。當他的14歲的女兒搬過來跟他一起住的時候，他得面對上班的問題還有照顧女兒的眾多問題。故事就是發生於肖恩的上班以及家庭生活展開。

==角色==
*[[肖恩·海斯|肖恩·海斯]] 飾演 肖恩(Sean Harrison)，男主角，一個離婚的同性戀者，在一間網路銷售公司上班，擔任主管。
*{{tsl|en|Linda Lavin|}} 飾演 蘿娜(Lorna)，肖恩的母親，經常過來幫忙照顧艾莉。
*[[莎曼沙·艾拉|莎曼沙·艾拉]] 飾演 艾莉(Ellie)，肖恩的14歲女兒。
*[[托馬斯·列儂|托馬斯·列儂]] 飾演 麥克斯(Max)，肖恩的新老闆，相當嚴厲。
*{{tsl|en|Megan Hilty|}} 飾演 莉茲(Liz)，肖恩的同事及女性朋友，經常給艾莉奇怪的女性建議。
*{{tsl|en|Echo Kellum|}} 飾演 杭特(Hunter)，肖恩的同事及朋友，有組樂團，但是很少看到他演出。

==製作過程==
本部作品於2012年12月決定製作，由[[肖恩·海斯|肖恩·海斯]] 擔任主角。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thefutoncritic.com/news/2012/12/19/development-update-wednesday-december-19-709410/10121/|title=Development Update: Wednesday, December 19|date=December 19, 2012|work=The Futon Critic|accessdate=September 28, 2013}}</ref> 在2013年1月22日，NBC決定製作本劇的試播集 ''Happiness''。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/01/22/development-update-tuesday-january-22-602404/10176/|title=Development Update: Tuesday, January 22|date=January 22, 2013|work=The Futon Critic|accessdate=September 28, 2013}}</ref> 試播集由{{tsl|en|Victor Fresco|}}編劇，{{tsl|en|James Burrows|}}導演。

在2013年2月開始宣布選角，除了男主角之外，宣布{{tsl|en|Linda Lavin|}}飾演蘿娜，肖恩的母親。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/02/linda-lavin-to-co-star-in-nbcs-sean-hayes-pilot-ann-dowd-recurs-on-masters-of-sex/|title=Linda Lavin To Co-Star In NBC’s Sean Hayes Pilot, Ann Dowd Recurs On ‘Masters Of Sex’|date=February 4, 2013|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=September 28, 2013|archive-date=2013-02-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EQS4XgCw?url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/02/linda-lavin-to-co-star-in-nbcs-sean-hayes-pilot-ann-dowd-recurs-on-masters-of-sex/|dead-url=no}}</ref> {{tsl|en|Echo Kellum|}}則是下一位被選出的演員，飾演杭特，肖恩的同事之一，喜歡音樂、攝影和詩歌。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/02/dave-annable-to-star-in-nbcs-joe-joe-jane-echo-kellum-joins-sean-hayes-pilot/|title=Dave Annable To Star In NBC’s ‘Joe, Joe & Jane’, Echo Kellum Joins Sean Hayes’ Pilot|date=February 6, 2013|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=September 28, 2013|archive-date=2014-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221225349/http://www.deadline.com/2013/02/dave-annable-to-star-in-nbcs-joe-joe-jane-echo-kellum-joins-sean-hayes-pilot/|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[托馬斯·列儂|托馬斯·列儂]] 隨後加入劇組，飾演麥克斯，肖恩的新老闆。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/thomas-lennon-nbc-sean-hayes-422063|title='Reno 911's' Thomas Lennon Joins NBC's Sean Hayes Comedy|date=February 18, 2013|last=Goldberg|first=Lesley|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=September 28, 2013|archive-date=2014-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314151157/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/thomas-lennon-nbc-sean-hayes-422063|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在2月底，[[莎曼沙·艾拉|莎曼沙·艾拉]]加入劇組飾演艾莉，肖恩的女兒。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/02/25/development-update-monday-february-25-606104/10221/|title=Development Update: Monday, February 25|date=February 25, 2013|work=The Futon Critic|accessdate=September 28, 2013}}</ref> 隨後宣布{{tsl|en|Lindsay Sloane|}}加入劇組飾演莉茲，肖恩的女同事與好朋友。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2013/02/26/sean-hayes-nbc-pilot-happiness-lindsay-sloane/|title=Exclusive: Lindsay Sloane Finds Happiness, Joins Sean Hayes' NBC Comedy Pilot|date=February 26, 2013|last=Ausiello|first=Michael|work=[[TV_Line|TV Line]]|accessdate=September 28, 2013|archive-date=2013-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231100921/http://tvline.com/2013/02/26/sean-hayes-nbc-pilot-happiness-lindsay-sloane/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 之後宣布[[维克·萨海|维克·萨海]]飾演配角豪爾(Howard)，一個IT技術員，與肖恩一同工作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/amy-aquino-to-co-star-in-abcs-divorce-seaton-smith-cast-in-nbcs-john-mulaney-project-more-pilot-castings/|title=Amy Aquino To Co-Star In ABC’s ‘Divorce’, Seaton Smith Cast In NBC’s John Mulaney Project & More Pilot Castings|date=April 8, 2013|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=September 28, 2013|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029191829/http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/amy-aquino-to-co-star-in-abcs-divorce-seaton-smith-cast-in-nbcs-john-mulaney-project-more-pilot-castings/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2013年5月9日，NBC宣布預定，並給予本系列的名稱為「肖恩的瘋狂世界」(''Sean Saves the World'')。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/nbc-series-orders-crisis-519604|title=NBC Series Orders: 'Crisis,' 'Believe,' 'About a Boy,' Sean Hayes, D.J. Nash Comedies|date=May 9, 2013|last=Goldberg|first=Lesley|last2=Rose|first2=Lacey|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=May 11, 2013|archive-date=2013-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608011822/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/nbc-series-orders-crisis-519604|dead-url=no}}</ref> 宣布預定的兩天後，Lindsay Sloane 宣布退出莉茲這個角色，因此很快地選出{{tsl|en|Megan Hilty|}}飾演莉茲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rewired.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/smash-reunion-megan-hilty-star-568409|title='Smash' Reunion: Megan Hilty to Co-Star in 'Sean Saves the World'|date=June 13, 2013|last=Goldberg|first=Lesley|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=June 13, 2013|archive-date=2013-06-15|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130615203945/http://rewired.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/smash-reunion-megan-hilty-star-568409|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 2013年11月8日，NBC宣布第一季增訂5集，因次第一季總共來到18集。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/11/nbcs-sean-saves-the-world-gets-order-for-five-more-episodes/|title=NBC’s ‘Sean Saves The World’ Gets Order For Five More Episodes|date=November 8, 2013|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=November 8, 2013|archive-date=2014-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320031732/http://www.deadline.com/2013/11/nbcs-sean-saves-the-world-gets-order-for-five-more-episodes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

